        <briefdescription>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Notify that the GL context has been re-created, e.g. after ReplaceSurface or Context loss.</para>
<para>In the case of ReplaceSurface, both ContextDestroyed() and ContextCreated() will have been called on the render thread before this is called on the event thread.</para>
<para>Multi-threading note: this method should be called from the main thread </para>
